{"tid":2008173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"監倉一位手足話「咪撚鬥黃、咪撚內鬨，我地入撚咗嚟，你地喺外面鬥黃做乜撚嘢」","createTime":"2020-05-08T23:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T09:49:14.000Z","uid":179775,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e672c050a04d87ba6005de900632f69ce6675e93","tid":2008173,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T23:59:55.000Z","msg":"From民主黨南區區議會主席羅健熙<br />\n<br />\n今朝去咗探一位手足，本來不打算特別講，但因為手足有說話想同喺外面既人分享，所以一定要打呢個post。<br />\n<br />\n手足在入面睇到資訊，知道早排有啲「鬥黃」事件。佢希望在外面的朋友們「咪撚鬥黃、咪撚內鬨，我地入撚咗嚟，你地喺外面鬥黃做乜撚嘢」。另外，佢對於民主派在立法會35+亦有期望，希望民主派一定要搞好初選，唔好好似上屆咁互相搶票，搞到何君堯入咗立法會，「如果因為搶票搞到輸撚咗贏唔到35+咁就真係對唔撚住我地」。<br />\n<br />\n佢亦都話，喺入面有同一位南非嚟既囚友傾偈，會同佢分享香港既情況。南非朋友聽完佢講之後寄語佢同香港人：「Don't Lose Hope」；手足亦希望用呢句說話寄語俾大家「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Don't Lose Hope</span></span>」！要繼續努力，唔可以就咁完咗。佢相信呢場運動，最重要最重要都係香港人自己。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 手足表示有時公務探訪的區議員朋友未必好知同佢講咩，佢話最好係可以分享多啲外面既資訊俾佢地知道"},{"pid":"f0db16163b975037dbddb6274bc056b02e3153d7","tid":2008173,"uid":106276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb058ac123e9cf0b5166a98840b576779a9370c","tid":2008173,"uid":67479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eeb736c2e25ff29661934719ace0d471bb28fec","tid":2008173,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c022bcac609197f66015a263c5705d076ee0314","tid":2008173,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c384c7b8d9759831fab27bdb56cdd304b3d8f35","tid":2008173,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:46:41.000Z","msg":"再鬥黃就要齊齊入去陪手足啦<br />\n內閧冇意思"},{"pid":"0fe50c02f0ac0f14594abca2141e27894392396e","tid":2008173,"uid":148204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db4060bca2bc41e5514cec152b6d502067f6616","tid":2008173,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:49:08.000Z","msg":"捉鬼=肅反<br />\n鬥黃=批鬥<br />\n<br />\n不捉鬼 不鬥黃"},{"pid":"3343e4a7e8e77023d3c8f4524488a1727e4e6f43","tid":2008173,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899e2d8d28d366fa83de5a9fbe60c5d802973c41","tid":2008173,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea483e3aa9c5eaa3409a98b7af78635bc7b176c","tid":2008173,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:50:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f21c37d3341f2a8e72c8ba404f1a2f5074230b16","tid":2008173,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:50:55.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n咪鬥<br />\n食m記<br />\n唔怕"},{"pid":"ed63744809d58525627d7c87f3495b668bd1ff18","tid":2008173,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:51:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3322b34a0ec9f3db66fb6624a40fdb059da65f49","tid":2008173,"uid":132027,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:52:07